	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I bought a cheap ebay famicom copy of gremlins 2 and it contains the sunsoft 5b chip.  Would it be possible to convert this into japanese mr. gimmick with the audio wired up?<br /><br />*edit*<br /><br />Looking at the maskroms the prg maskrom of gremlins 2 has less pins haha d'oh.  I also have a batman return of the joker, would it be easier desoldering the 5b and installing it in my return of the joker nes cart?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
